{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"3c963d8f8b","title":"对李富春关于起草追脏问题文件的来信的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8c10ac86bd","index":0,"year":1952,"month":2,"day":29,"articleId":"3c963d8f8b"}],"tags":[{"id":"25e2abfb25","name":"李富春","type":"人物"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji31","name":"毛泽东全集第31卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/31-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji31":{"comments":[{"id":"131b82dee1","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"3c963d8f8b","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"李富春，当时任政务院财政经济委员会副主任、中央人民政府节约检查委员会副主任。"},{"id":"5e905a20c1","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"3c963d8f8b","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指李富春起草的关于追脏问题的文件初稿。他在1952年2月27日写给毛泽东的信中说，这个文件有两个重点：一是“严肃地贯彻中央政策，凡是确定为贫污犯者（五十万元以下者已决定不算贪污，我还主张一百万元以下者不算贪污），分别情况处理”。二是“姓款归谁接收，公款一律归国库，群众性的款物分别交还原主”。"},{"id":"2390751c42","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"3c963d8f8b","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"彭真，当时任中共北京市委书记、中央人民政府节约检查委员会副主任。"}],"contents":[{"id":"26f7512b32","type":"title","text":"对李富春\"关于起草追脏问题文件的来信的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"3c963d8f8b"},{"id":"131b82dee1","type":"paragraph","text":"周总理：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"3c963d8f8b"},{"id":"5e905a20c1","type":"paragraph","text":"此件须加修改，请你处理，并请与彭真商的，吸收北京市的经验。此外，关于百万元以下的人大部予以解脱，宜发一电示，亦请你的定。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"3c963d8f8b"},{"id":"2390751c42","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"3c963d8f8b"},{"id":"ace711c681","type":"paragraph","text":"二月廿九日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"3c963d8f8b"}],"page":{"id":"0efa3730be","publi